# alert-crawler layer constraints
#
# Layer boundaries are enforced by `task layers:check`.
# A package at layer N may only import packages at layer < N.
# Use `allow SOURCE TARGET` to document known violations pending resolution.

# L0: Foundation — no internal imports allowed
0 config
0 domain

# L1: Adapters and Infrastructure wrappers — may import L0 only
1 adapter
1 adapter/rss
1 catalogue
1 elasticsearch
1 redis
1 severity
1 scope
1 observability

# L2: Orchestration — may import L0 and L1
2 runner
